            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Jeremiah.35:1-36:32",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EJeremiah%2035%3A1-36%3A32%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_35_1%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJeremiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E35%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Faithful%20Recabites%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20message%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20gave%20Jeremiah%20when%20Jehoiakim%20son%20of%20Josiah%20was%20king%20of%20Judah%3A%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_35_2%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BGo%20to%20the%20settlement%20where%20the%20families%20of%20the%20Recabites%20live%2C%20and%20invite%20them%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Temple.%20Take%20them%20into%20one%20of%20the%20inner%20rooms%2C%20and%20offer%20them%20some%20wine.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_35_3%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20I%20went%20to%20see%20Jaazaniah%20son%20of%20Jeremiah%20and%20grandson%20of%20Habazziniah%20and%20all%20his%20brothers%20and%20sons%26%23x2014%3Brepresenting%20all%20the%20Recabite%20families.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_35_4%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20took%20them%20to%20the%20Temple%2C%20and%20we%20went%20into%20the%20room%20assigned%20to%20the%20sons%20of%20Hanan%20son%20of%20Igdaliah%2C%20a%20man%20of%20God.%20This%20room%20was%20located%20next%20to%20the%20one%20used%20by%20the%20Temple%20officials%2C%20directly%20above%20the%20room%20of%20Maaseiah%20son%20of%20Shallum%2C%20the%20Temple%20gatekeeper.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_35_5%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20set%20cups%20and%20jugs%20of%20wine%20before%20them%20and%20invited%20them%20to%20have%20a%20drink%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_35_6%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3Ebut%20they%20refused.%20%26%23x201C%3BNo%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20they%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3Bwe%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20drink%20wine%2C%20because%20our%20ancestor%20Jehonadab%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E35%3A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EJonadab%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20variant%20spelling%20of%20Jehonadab%3B%20also%20in%2035%3A10%2C%2019.%20See%202%26%23xA0%3BKgs%2010%3A15.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20son%20of%20Recab%20gave%20us%20this%20command%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BYou%20and%20your%20descendants%20must%20never%20drink%20wine.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_35_7%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20do%20not%20build%20houses%20or%20plant%20crops%20or%20vineyards%2C%20but%20always%20live%20in%20tents.%20If%20you%20follow%20these%20commands%2C%20you%20will%20live%20long%2C%20good%20lives%20in%20the%20land.%26%23x2019%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_35_8%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20we%20have%20obeyed%20him%20in%20all%20these%20things.%20We%20have%20never%20had%20a%20drink%20of%20wine%20to%20this%20day%2C%20nor%20have%20our%20wives%2C%20our%20sons%2C%20or%20our%20daughters.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_35_9%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EWe%20haven%26%23x2019%3Bt%20built%20houses%20or%20owned%20vineyards%20or%20farms%20or%20planted%20crops.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_35_10%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EWe%20have%20lived%20in%20tents%20and%20have%20fully%20obeyed%20all%20the%20commands%20of%20Jehonadab%2C%20our%20ancestor.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_35_11%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20when%20King%20Nebuchadnezzar%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E35%3A11a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3ENebuchadrezzar%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20variant%20spelling%20of%20Nebuchadnezzar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Babylon%20attacked%20this%20country%2C%20we%20were%20afraid%20of%20the%20Babylonian%20and%20Syrian%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E35%3A11b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3EChaldean%20and%20Aramean.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20armies.%20So%20we%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20Jerusalem.%20That%20is%20why%20we%20are%20here.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_35_12%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20gave%20this%20message%20to%20Jeremiah%3A%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_35_13%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20says%3A%20Go%20and%20say%20to%20the%20people%20in%20Judah%20and%20Jerusalem%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BCome%20and%20learn%20a%20lesson%20about%20how%20to%20obey%20me.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_35_14%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20Recabites%20do%20not%20drink%20wine%20to%20this%20day%20because%20their%20ancestor%20Jehonadab%20told%20them%20not%20to.%20But%20I%20have%20spoken%20to%20you%20again%20and%20again%2C%20and%20you%20refuse%20to%20obey%20me.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_35_15%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3ETime%20after%20time%20I%20sent%20you%20prophets%2C%20who%20told%20you%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BTurn%20from%20your%20wicked%20ways%2C%20and%20start%20doing%20things%20right.%20Stop%20worshiping%20other%20gods%20so%20that%20you%20might%20live%20in%20peace%20here%20in%20the%20land%20I%20have%20given%20to%20you%20and%20your%20ancestors.%26%23x201D%3B%20But%20you%20would%20not%20listen%20to%20me%20or%20obey%20me.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_35_16%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20descendants%20of%20Jehonadab%20son%20of%20Recab%20have%20obeyed%20their%20ancestor%20completely%2C%20but%20you%20have%20refused%20to%20listen%20to%20me.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_35_17%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BTherefore%2C%20this%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20God%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20says%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BBecause%20you%20refuse%20to%20listen%20or%20answer%20when%20I%20call%2C%20I%20will%20send%20upon%20Judah%20and%20Jerusalem%20all%20the%20disasters%20I%20have%20threatened.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_35_18%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Jeremiah%20turned%20to%20the%20Recabites%20and%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20says%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BYou%20have%20obeyed%20your%20ancestor%20Jehonadab%20in%20every%20respect%2C%20following%20all%20his%20instructions.%26%23x2019%3B%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_35_19%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2235%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3ETherefore%2C%20this%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20says%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BJehonadab%20son%20of%20Recab%20will%20always%20have%20descendants%20who%20serve%20me.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_36_1%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJeremiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E36%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EBaruch%20Reads%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22subhead-sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Messages%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EDuring%20the%20fourth%20year%20that%20Jehoiakim%20son%20of%20Josiah%20was%20king%20in%20Judah%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E36%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20fourth%20year%20of%20Jehoiakim%26%23x2019%3Bs%20reign%20was%20605%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-sc%22%3Eb.c.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20gave%20this%20message%20to%20Jeremiah%3A%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_36_2%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BGet%20a%20scroll%2C%20and%20write%20down%20all%20my%20messages%20against%20Israel%2C%20Judah%2C%20and%20the%20other%20nations.%20Begin%20with%20the%20first%20message%20back%20in%20the%20days%20of%20Josiah%2C%20and%20write%20down%20every%20message%2C%20right%20up%20to%20the%20present%20time.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_36_3%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EPerhaps%20the%20people%20of%20Judah%20will%20repent%20when%20they%20hear%20again%20all%20the%20terrible%20things%20I%20have%20planned%20for%20them.%20Then%20I%20will%20be%20able%20to%20forgive%20their%20sins%20and%20wrongdoings.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_36_4%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Jeremiah%20sent%20for%20Baruch%20son%20of%20Neriah%2C%20and%20as%20Jeremiah%20dictated%20all%20the%20prophecies%20that%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20had%20given%20him%2C%20Baruch%20wrote%20them%20on%20a%20scroll.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_36_5%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Jeremiah%20said%20to%20Baruch%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20am%20a%20prisoner%20here%20and%20unable%20to%20go%20to%20the%20Temple.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_36_6%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20you%20go%20to%20the%20Temple%20on%20the%20next%20day%20of%20fasting%2C%20and%20read%20the%20messages%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20that%20I%20have%20had%20you%20write%20on%20this%20scroll.%20Read%20them%20so%20the%20people%20who%20are%20there%20from%20all%20over%20Judah%20will%20hear%20them.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_36_7%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EPerhaps%20even%20yet%20they%20will%20turn%20from%20their%20evil%20ways%20and%20ask%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20forgiveness%20before%20it%20is%20too%20late.%20For%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20threatened%20them%20with%20his%20terrible%20anger.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_36_8%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EBaruch%20did%20as%20Jeremiah%20told%20him%20and%20read%20these%20messages%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20to%20the%20people%20at%20the%20Temple.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_36_9%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20did%20this%20on%20a%20day%20of%20sacred%20fasting%20held%20in%20late%20autumn%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E36%3A9%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ein%20the%20ninth%20month%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20ancient%20Hebrew%20lunar%20calendar%20(also%20in%2036%3A22).%20The%20ninth%20month%20in%20the%20fifth%20year%20of%20Jehoiakim%26%23x2019%3Bs%20reign%20occurred%20within%20the%20months%20of%20November%20and%20December%20604%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-sc%22%3Eb.c.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Also%20see%20note%20on%201%3A3.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20during%20the%20fifth%20year%20of%20the%20reign%20of%20Jehoiakim%20son%20of%20Josiah.%20People%20from%20all%20over%20Judah%20had%20come%20to%20Jerusalem%20to%20attend%20the%20ser