2C%20to%20ask%20Baruch%20to%20come%20and%20read%20the%20messages%20to%20them%2C%20too.%20So%20Baruch%20took%20the%20scroll%20and%20went%20to%20them.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_36_15%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSit%20down%20and%20read%20the%20scroll%20to%20us%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20the%20officials%20said%2C%20and%20Baruch%20did%20as%20they%20requested.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_36_16%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20they%20heard%20all%20the%20messages%2C%20they%20looked%20at%20one%20another%20in%20alarm.%20%26%23x201C%3BWe%20must%20tell%20the%20king%20what%20we%20have%20heard%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20they%20said%20to%20Baruch.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_36_17%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBut%20first%2C%20tell%20us%20how%20you%20got%20these%20messages.%20Did%20they%20come%20directly%20from%20Jeremiah%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_36_18%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Baruch%20explained%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BJeremiah%20dictated%20them%2C%20and%20I%20wrote%20them%20down%20in%20ink%2C%20word%20for%20word%2C%20on%20this%20scroll.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_36_19%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2236%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BYou%20and%20Jeremiah%20should%20both%20hide%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20the%20officials%20told%20Baruch.%20%26%23x201C%3BDon%26%23x2019%3Bt%20tell%20anyone%20where%20you%